The full Windows installer package is hosted externally because the bundled local AI models make the release larger than GitHub’s per-file release asset limit.

Download:

ModuTone-1.0.0-windows-x64.zip from: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1bYFJQ5fX_y2y_9VmVBwiQuJp1i1YcgjI/view?usp=drive_link

After downloading:

Extract the ZIP.
Keep these two files in the same folder:
ModuTone_1.0.0_x64-setup.exe
ModuTone_1.0.0_x64-setup.7z
Run ModuTone_1.0.0_x64-setup.exe.
Follow the installer prompts.
The .7z payload contains the bundled local GGUF models required by ModuTone. Do not rename or move it before running the installer.
